overview: For the 65 time Live traditional New Year's concert from the beautiful Musikverein in Vienna.  The concert, broadcast in 90 countries and reaching an audience of over 40 million people, features, as usual, polkas, waltzes and overtures from the Strauss clan and their contemporaries.  For the third time, the Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra is led by the conductor Franz Welser-MÃ¶st and the Vienna Children's Choir also participates.  Swedish commentator: Camilla Lundberg.
title: Neujahrskonzert der Wiener Philharmoniker 2023
